12
00:00:38,335 --> 00:00:43,374
s'zaynen arayn di tsvey partizaner mitn zak in mashine un mir zaynen avekgeforn vayter.

13
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:45,163
ir veyst di tsvey partizaner, ver zaynen zey geven?

14
00:00:45,338 --> 00:00:46,690
kh'ken zey nit.

15
00:00:46,148 --> 00:00:46,901
neyn.

16
00:00:46,690 --> 00:00:47,559
neyn.

17
00:00:47,076 --> 00:00:50,428
dos iz far aykh geven, zaynen zey geven der u- umbakante mentshn.

18
00:00:49,557 --> 00:00:50,901
umbakante.

19
00:00:50,772 --> 00:00:55,508
un der partizan, der vegvayzer vos hot gezesn lebn SHOFЁR iz geven far aykh a bakanter?

20
00:00:56,053 --> 00:00:58,983
