35
00:01:39,942 --> 00:01:42,267
un m'iz avek tsu fus dortn,

36
00:01:42,460 --> 00:01:46,369
velder. Endlin hot undz avekgefirt in baze.

37
00:01:43,270 --> 00:01:44,124
un,

38
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:48,140
