137
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:28,872
me flegt lign di gantse tsayt un zikh ⟨eynem on der andern⟩ raybn.

138
00:06:29,098 --> 00:06:33,850
me flegt in di fri oyfshteyn, aroysgeyn oyfn gas, vinter-tsayt arunternemen di hemder

139
00:06:33,850 --> 00:06:37,120
un hakn on di beymer, s'zoln a⟨runter⟩faln di layz.

140
00:06:36,827 --> 00:06:38,154
