146
00:06:58,663 --> 00:07:00,732
oyf shlakh- oyf oyfgabes, ya?

147
00:07:00,233 --> 00:07:01,712
oyf oyfgabes, ye.

148
00:07:02,916 --> 00:07:06,370
oyfgabes iz geven zeyer fil. zeyer fil.

149
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:10,910
⟨,⟩ ikh hob do farshribn, ⟨ikh⟩ UNK ⟨nit,⟩ er zogt az me ken nit,......

150
00:07:11,404 --> 00:07:16,241
vos gedenkt ir per- far a oyfgabes vos ir, ir hot, ir hot genumen aynteyl ⟨in,...⟩?

151
00:07:15,336 --> 00:07:17,777
oyfgabe iz geven, s'iz geven,

152
00:07:18,475 --> 00:07:23,531
arum undz iz geven, umgefer draysik kilometer iz geven a PARTIZANSK⟨AYA⟩...

153
00:07:23,402 --> 00:07:24,341
zone.

154
00:07:23,858 --> 00:07:24,892
zone.

155
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:26,060
partizanishe z-...

156
