157
00:07:28,093 --> 00:07:31,794
zey hobn gevust az dortn veln zey ge- ge- krign dem toyt, ⟨az zey veln⟩ arayn in di zone.

158
00:07:31,794 --> 00:07:37,480
vayter iz geven blotes dortn, az s'iz geven ummeglekh tsutsukumen tsu undz.

159
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:41,380
mernit vi di partizaner hobn gevust vu, nu, vu me ken zikh durkhgeyn.

160
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:44,980
oyb a mentsh hot nit gevust, ⟨flegt er⟩ glaykh araynzinken biz danen dortn.

161
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:53,366
 s'iz geven arum, geven arum, geven zeyer fil, g-, di,...

162
