163
00:07:58,705 --> 00:08:00,488
un undzer tsil iz geven

164
00:08:00,628 --> 00:08:02,005
zey tsu farnikhtn.

165
00:08:02,974 --> 00:08:05,972
undz h- eyn mol hot men undz geshikt farnikhtn a garnizon,

166
