00:19:25,939 --> 00:19:28,080
ir flegt dos baytn gever oyf gever?

392
00:19:28,080 --> 00:19:30,000
me flegt aykh baytn eyn min geve-...?

393
00:19:29,010 --> 00:19:32,290
es flegt onkumen naye gever, flegt men glaykh baytn,

394
00:19:32,290 --> 00:19:34,939
flegt men glaykh tsunemen glaykh di alte un gebn naye.

395
00:19:34,939 --> 00:19:37,290
glaykh gebn naye gever flegt men glaykh gebn.

396
00:19:38,612 --> 00:19:42,858
azoy arum az, s'iz, s'iz geven ge- patrones hobn mir shoyn gehat,...

397
00:19:42,325 --> 00:19:43,736
koyln a sakh, ye?

398
00:19:43,388 --> 00:19:45,300
zeyer fil koyln iz geven,

399
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:48,900
zeyer fil geven AVTOMATn, zeyer fil geven...

400
00:19:49,125 --> 00:19:52,257
granatn iz geven. alts hobn mir shoyn gehat dan.

401
00:19:52,298 --> 00:19:56,899
dos iz shoyn ober geven zeyer shpet, letst⟨- dos iz⟩ geven...

402
00:19:57,985 --> 00:20:01,590
ir gedenkt di letste vokhn in ayer partizanishe makhne,

403
00:20:01,849 --> 00:20:03,969
vi zey zaynen oysgekumen, di letste vokhn?

404
00:20:04,144 --> 00:20:06,129
d- di letste vokhn?

405
00:20:07,452 --> 00:20:09,251
di letste vokhn,

406
00:20:09,932 --> 00:20:12,288
 az der front hot zikh shoyn dernentert,

407
00:20:12,548 --> 00:20:16,406
hot men genumen arunterlozn desantn, desantnikes, di rusn,

408
00:20:16,986 --> 00:20:18,296
bay undz in vald.

409
00:20:19,045 --> 00:20:27,720
un mir hobn dortn gevust ale, ale vegn, ale sh- vu me darf durkhgeyn. flegn mir geyn mit zey als oysshpirer, flegn mir zey zogn az

410
00:20:22,808 --> 00:20:23,780
shte⟨k⟩n.

411
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:33,197
do darf men geyn, un do darf men geyn, vayl zey hobn gedarft makhn plener vu di, di armey zol kenen durkhgeyn nokh dem.

412
00:20:34,485 --> 00:20:36,419
nu, mir zaynen...

413
00:20:41,083 --> 00:20:45,800
eyn mol hobn mir gekhapt,

414
00:20:45,910 --> 00:20:49,310
a daytshishe grupe iz gegangen. s'iz geven,

415
00:20:49,310 --> 00:20:55,860
dos iz geven zumer, shoyn geven hoykh gevaksn di, di, tvue, di korn,

416
00:20:55,933 --> 00:21:03,284
hobn zikh dortn geshart daytshishe soldatn. zey hobn derzen az lebn, do iz do rusishe soldatn un partizaner.

417
00:21:03,477 --> 00:21:08,162
mir hobn zey, me hot zey bamerkt un m'hot zey alemen arumgeringlt un m'hot zey alemen

418
00:21:08,320 --> 00:21:11,081
dershosn, un andere hot men farvundet.

419
00:21:11,104 --> 00:21:13,716
bay undz iz geven eyne a krankn-shvester.

420
00:21:13,716 --> 00:21:17,746
zi flegt, zeltn geyn oyf, operatsyes.

421
00:21:17,803 --> 00:21:20,760
zi iz geven nor in UNK dortn iz zi geven oyf an ort.

422
00:21:19,778 --> 00:21:21,071
oyf der baze.

423
00:21:20,760 --> 00:21:22,027
oyf der baze iz zi geven.

424
00:21:22,027 --> 00:21:25,762
nu, hot zi eyn mol ongebetn, zi vil khotshe eynem dershisn.

425
00:21:25,819 --> 00:21:32,140
hot men gebrakht eynem a daytshn un m'hot ir gegebn di ⟨DO-⟩ di, dem fargenign, zi zol dershisn dem daytshn,

426
00:21:32,140 --> 00:21:34,638
s'zol zayn oyf ir SCHЁT oykh a derhargeter...

427
00:21:33,666 --> 00:21:37,254
oyf ir kheshbn a derhargeter daytsh. dos iz geven a yidishe krankn-shve-...?

428
00:21:36,349 --> 00:21:38,202
a yidishe, ya, a yidishe.

429
00:21:38,202 --> 00:21:39,887
 eyn mol iz geven a fal,

430
00:21:40,220 --> 00:21:43,312
, m'iz gegangen oyf a...

431
00:21:43,048 --> 00:21:44,240
oyfgabe.

432
00:21:43,622 --> 00:21:44,831
oyfgabe,

433
00:21:45,377 --> 00:21:49,590
un eynem a yidishn yingl hot men zeyer shver farvundet a fus,

434
00:21:49,647 --> 00:21:50,822
zeyer shver.

435
00:21:51,975 --> 00:21:57,521
er iz geven a g- fester, gezunter yat. nu, m'hot im gebrakht tsu firn in baze.

436
00:21:57,595 --> 00:22:02,865
keyn doktoyrim hobn mir nit gehat. keyn medikamentn iz kimet, kimat oykh nit geven.

437
00:22:02,865 --> 00:22:04,929
di eyntsike krankn-shvester iz geven.

438
00:22:05,020 --> 00:22:07,143
m'hot im gevelt ober zeyer rateven.

439
00:22:07,143 --> 00:22:09,418
un di fus iz geven zeyer tse-...

440
00:22:09,360 --> 00:22:10,430
 tseshtert.

441
00:22:09,998 --> 00:22:14,025
tseshtert, ya. m'hot im gemuzt umbadingt opshnaydn di fus.

442
00:22:14,537 --> 00:22:19,728
vos zol men ton? bashlosn, mit a poshete zegele hot men im di fus opgeshnitn,

443
00:22:20,460 --> 00:22:23,677
on a narkoz, un er hot dos alts ⟨durkhge-⟩ durkhgetrogn.

444
00:22:25,472 --> 00:22:32,520
nu, der sof iz geven az er hot keyn mazl nit gehat tsu blaybn lebn. er iz umgekumen.

445
00:22:32,256 --> 00:22:34,562
ir veyst di familye fun dem partizan?

446
00:22:34,416 --> 00:22:38,949
ikh veys nit. fargesn. ikh gedenk vi er shteyt mir far di oygn shteyt er mir.

447
00:22:37,791 --> 00:22:40,232
un der nomen fun di krankn-shvester veyst ir?

448
00:22:45,537 --> 00:22:47,606
ober zi iz geven a yidishe, fun Kovner...?

449
00:22:46,735 --> 00:22:48,349
 a yidishe, a yidishe, ye.

450
00:22:48,760 --> 00:22:53,890
nu, nokh, kumendik fun Kovne iz zi, iz zi avekgeforn in, in Shavl mitn man.

451
00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:57,150
der man iz oykh geven a partizan. dortn iz er gevorn a direktor fun,

452
00:22:57,150 --> 00:22:59,300
fun, bir,...

453
00:22:58,817 --> 00:22:59,789
KOMBINAT.

454
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:04,566
KOMBINAT in Shavl. fargesn di familye zeyere. ⟨s'iz avek⟩ a tsayt yorn.

455
00:23:04,453 --> 00:23:07,619
yo. un, vi hot ir zikh fareynikt mit der sovyetisher armey?

456
00:23:08,520 --> 00:23:10,533
nu, beshas zey hobn shoyn genumen

457
00:23:10,533 --> 00:23:13,594
ongrayfn UNK ⟨dernent⟩ zikh shoyn tsu Lite,

458
00:23:14,443 --> 00:23:16,799
nu, hobn mir zikh fareynikt mit zey.

459
00:23:16,992 --> 00:23:19,787
vu hot ir zikh, fareynikt mit zey, in vos far a gegnt?

460
00:23:21,379 --> 00:23:26,739
zey hobn genumen geyn mit zaytike vegn hobn zey genumen geyn, di, di, di daytshishe armey.

461
00:23:27,066 --> 00:23:28,562
hobn mir zikh glaykh

462
00:23:28,652 --> 00:23:31,548
dernentert tsu zey. zey hobn undz derkont.

463
00:23:31,639 --> 00:23:33,000
vayter...

464
00:23:31,842 --> 00:23:35,396
dos iz mistome di sovyetishe armey iz genumen geyn mit dayt- mit zaytike vegn?

465
00:23:35,723 --> 00:23:36,932
tsu di daytshishe?

466
00:23:35,757 --> 00:23:38,100
ye, di, di sovyetishe,

467
00:23:38,100 --> 00:23:42,433
vayle di daytshn hobn shoyn genumen OTSTUPA-, hobn genumen shoyn ⟨ant- o-⟩ optretn.

468
00:23:40,380 --> 00:23:41,842
op- optretn.

469
00:23:42,726 --> 00:23:45,730
zaynen di daytshn geforn mitn, mit di,

470
00:23:45,055 --> 00:23:46,179
hoypt-vegn.

471
00:23:45,730 --> 00:23:47,107
mit di gute veg,

472
00:23:47,299 --> 00:23:51,427
un di rusishe armey hobn shoyn genumen zey ringlen fun zayt.

473
00:23:50,995 --> 00:23:51,934
fun zayt.

474
00:23:51,855 --> 00:23:54,026
nu, hobn mir zikh glaykh mit ir fareynikt

475
00:23:54,066 --> 00:24:01,772
un mir hobn geholfn mit, mit di, mit di rusishe armey traybn di daytshn vos vayter biz, biz Vilne.

476
00:24:02,267 --> 00:24:04,336
ir zayt a- ir zayt arayn in Vilne?

477
00:24:04,039 --> 00:24:05,568
arayn in Vilne, ye.

478
00:24:05,153 --> 00:24:07,847
ir zayt geven tsvishn di velkhe zaynen arayn in Vilne?

479
00:24:06,908 --> 00:24:09,920
ya. mir zaynen arayn in Vilne.

480
00:24:10,232 --> 00:24:18,647
in Vilne hot men genumen sorti- hot men genumen bashtetikn UNK zeyer fil hobn zey gebetn vayter geyn oyfn front tsum kemfn.

481
00:24:19,547 --> 00:24:23,480
undz hot men genumen, m'hot gedarft hobn naye, naye, nu,

482
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:30,003
kadern do in Lite. ⟨keyn, in ergets iz keyn zakh do⟩ nit geven; ⟨do iz nokh⟩ alts, alts geven di, S- SMETONOVSKe...

483
00:24:30,162 --> 00:24:31,286
kadern, ye?

484
00:24:30,870 --> 00:24:36,723
kadern. nu, hot men gelozn, mir hot men ibergelozn do in Lite. m'hot mir bashtimt

485
00:24:37,710 --> 00:24:42,524
vayter tsum kemfn mit, mit di banditn in di velder.

486
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:47,216
un ir, far, Vilne, hot ir, aleyn gekemft, far Vilne?

487
00:24:47,290 --> 00:24:52,583
baym ba- far bafrayen Vilne hot ayer, partizanishe makhne gekemft, ge- genumen aynteyl in kamf?

488
00:24:51,407 --> 00:24:59,470
ye. mir zaynen arayn biz Vilne, un nokh dem hot men undz geheysn geyn durkh Kazlove-Rude. undz hot men glaykh opgeteylt, undzer OTRYAD, un m'hot undz geheysn geyn durkh Kazlove-Rude,

489
00:24:59,470 --> 00:25:04,006
un nokh dem kumen in Kovne durkh Aleksoter zayt hot men undz geheysn kumen in Kovne.

490
00:25:03,709 --> 00:25:08,208
un vi s'iz aykh, vi s'iz aykh gelungen tsu, durkhgeyn biz Kazlove-Rude?

491
00:25:08,620 --> 00:25:10,065
durkh velder.

492
00:25:09,885 --> 00:25:12,731
un, vi, vi zayt ir durkhgegangen dem Nyemen?

493
00:25:13,277 --> 00:25:16,990
der Nemen iz geven, komish,.

494
00:25:16,990 --> 00:25:19,329
keyn lotkes iz nit geven. keyn...

495
00:25:18,492 --> 00:25:19,819
keyn shiflekh, ya?

496
00:25:19,453 --> 00:25:25,980
⟨shi- mi-⟩ shiflekh. mir flegn geyn dortn bay di breges un, un oyfzukhn a shifl, flegt men arayngeyn in ir tsvey man, dray man.

497
00:25:25,980 --> 00:25:32,424
di ershte hot men aribergehoybn mit di koyln-varfers glaykh. zey hobn glaykh zey geleygt oyfn ander breg⟨e⟩ dortn.

498
00:25:31,519 --> 00:25:33,335
dos iz geven bay nakht tsu bay tog?

499
00:25:33,443 --> 00:25:35,850
dos iz geven in der fri iz dos geven.

500
00:25:35,923 --> 00:25:39,500
geven a zeyger fir mistome. s'iz geven likhtik UNK.

501
00:25:39,990 --> 00:25:44,280
di ershte zaynen ariber, ⟨zay- di er-⟩ aribergeforn mit di koyln-varfers,

502
00:25:44,280 --> 00:25:47,510
eyner Pasternyak, un nokh dem iz geven nokh eyner, ⟨kh'gedenk nit dem...⟩

503
00:25:46,386 --> 00:25:48,624
Pasternak, dos iz a nomen fun a partizan?

504
00:25:48,107 --> 00:25:50,050
ya. er iz geve-...

505
00:25:48,715 --> 00:25:50,227
er iz geven fun Kovne?

506
00:25:50,050 --> 00:25:51,650
er iz geven a Kovner, ya.

507
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:54,800
er iz geven a, pulemyotshik.

508
00:25:54,638 --> 00:25:56,488
a ⟨k-⟩ mit a koyln-varfer...

509
00:25:55,633 --> 00:25:57,264
mit a koyln-varfer, ya.

510
00:25:57,490 --> 00:26:00,673
nokh dem hot men a- genumen ariberheybn di gantse...

511
00:26:00,561 --> 00:26:01,753
alemen, ya?

512
00:26:01,168 --> 00:26:03,710
alemen, ya. UNK

513
00:26:02,485 --> 00:26:04,301
vi hot ir zikh aribergehoybn?

514
00:26:05,168 --> 00:26:09,720
m'hot tsu tsvey, ver ⟨s'hot gekent⟩ shvimen hot geshvumen. me flegt zikh onhaltn,

515
00:26:09,720 --> 00:26:15,040
tsvey zaynen gezesn in lotke, tsvey ⟨zay-⟩ hobn zikh ongehaltn un, un m'hot, m'hot zey nokhge- ⟨shoyn⟩ nokhgeshlept.

516
00:26:14,263 --> 00:26:15,843
ir hot gekent shvimen?

517
00:26:15,040 --> 00:26:17,095
di gant-... kh'hob gekent gut shvimen.

518
00:26:17,048 --> 00:26:18,037
ir⟨, ir⟩...

519
00:26:17,095 --> 00:26:21,390
ikh bin aleyn geborn in Zaras- ikh bin aleyn a Zarasayer un ikh hob gelebt lebn a ozere.

520
00:26:18,913 --> 00:26:19,913
UNK

521
00:26:21,390 --> 00:26:23,066
shvimen shvim ikh zeyer gut.

522
00:26:22,701 --> 00:26:25,715
iz ir hot geshvumen aleyn, tsu ir zayt gezesn in lotke?

523
00:26:25,198 --> 00:26:26,424
ikh bin geshvumen.

524
00:26:26,363 --> 00:26:28,196
o- zikh onhaltndik tsu...?

525
00:26:27,443 --> 00:26:33,124
ongehaltn, tsvey man hobn mir zikh ongehaltn un di lotke hot men ge-... un mir zaynen UNK ariberge⟨hoyb⟩n oyfn ander zayt.

526
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:37,080
ir, ir, ir hot zikh oysgeton di begodim farn shv-, sh-...?

527
00:26:36,049 --> 00:26:42,080
vo- keyn zakh nit oysgeton: mit begodim. ver hot dan gekukt begodim, ver? m'iz ⟨M-⟩ nas, ge- gegosn, ⟨v- ikh...⟩

528
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:46,657
m'hot mernit di gever arayngeleygt in lotke un ⟨e-⟩ m'hot zikh ongehaltn un m'hot aribergehoybn oyf di ander zayt.

529
00:26:46,714 --> 00:26:50,758
m'hot aribergehoybn dan a b- draysik man ⟨hot men⟩ aribergehoybn. dos hot gedoyert,

530
00:26:50,899 --> 00:26:52,243
dos hot gedoyert...

531
00:26:52,688 --> 00:26:55,955
ye, un nokh dem, ⟨ersht⟩ ariber oyfn ander zayt,

532
00:26:56,029 --> 00:26:58,770
hot men undz dershmekt.

533
00:26:58,662 --> 00:26:59,719
di daytshn?

534
00:26:59,472 --> 00:27:05,070
di daytshn ⟨oder di, L-⟩ Litv- di Litvi- Litviner. dershmekt undz.

535
00:27:05,125 --> 00:27:11,649
hobn zey... un mir hobn gedarft aribergeyn a brikl hobn mir gedarft aribergeyn. dos iz geven a bisl vayter N- vi der Nemen.

536
00:27:11,892 --> 00:27:15,008
hobn zey gemakht a... lebn brikl...

537
00:27:14,473 --> 00:27:15,699
a loyerung.

538
00:27:15,132 --> 00:27:16,537
a loyerung

539
00:27:16,537 --> 00:27:24,035
un zey hobn gevart oyf undz. un ikh bin dan grade geven, gegangen der ershter in oysshpir-grupe bin ikh geven. gegangen zeks man zaynen mir gegangen.

540
00:27:24,092 --> 00:27:29,380
undz hot men aribergelozn. zey hobn gevust az hintn UNK geyt der gantser OTRYAD zeyer fil.

541
00:27:29,380 --> 00:27:33,420
undz hot men aribergelozn; undz hot men keyn zakh nit getshepet. mir zaynen ariber zeyer gut.

542
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:38,294
vi nor s'iz aroyf der, di gantse grupe oyfn brik, hobn zey geefnt a fayer.

543
00:27:38,638 --> 00:27:41,838
dershosn dem komandir's,

544
00:27:41,862 --> 00:27:44,353
froy hot men dershosn, Tseyko's.

545
00:27:45,220 --> 00:27:48,167
eynem hot men zeyer shver ge- ge- farvundet.

546
00:27:48,814 --> 00:27:54,290
nu, nokh dem hobn mir zikh, gehat opgeshtelt.

547
00:27:54,585 --> 00:27:58,170
mir hobn geefnt a fayer tsurik, un s'iz gevorn nokh dem shtil.

548
00:27:58,348 --> 00:28:00,924
nokh dem, az mir zaynen arayn in vald,

549
00:28:01,099 --> 00:28:04,110
hot der Tseyko gezogt,

550
00:28:04,356 --> 00:28:09,142
"vu iz ahingekumen, di o OLYA," hot, OL'GA hot zi geheysn.

551
00:28:09,148 --> 00:28:12,080
dos iz geven zayn vayb⟨, a⟩ gelibte; s'iz nit vikhtik UNK.

552
00:28:12,270 --> 00:28:13,681
"vu iz zi ahingekumen?"

553
00:28:13,958 --> 00:28:20,617
ikh shtey grade lebn im. zogt er, "Koblents, du, du un du, gey zu- zofort gey z- zukht ir oyfet."

554
00:28:21,045 --> 00:28:25,831
mir zaynen glaykh arunter. mir gibn a kuk: zi ligt oyfn brik, oysgetsoygn

555
00:28:25,939 --> 00:28:28,040
vi a plakhe, toyte.

556
00:28:28,588 --> 00:28:32,682
mir hobn ir genumen trogn. shver iz geven; zi iz geven zeyer a, a...

557
00:28:32,132 --> 00:28:32,973
a fule.

558
00:28:32,689 --> 00:28:34,220
a fule iz zi geven.

559
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:37,020
zalbe firt hobn mir zeyer shver ir getrogn.

560
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:40,570
mir hobn zeyer shver ir getrogn zalbe firt.

561
00:28:40,570 --> 00:28:43,229
mit a mol hobn mir gezen az fun vaytn,

562
00:28:43,489 --> 00:28:47,070
fun vaytn forn mashines ⟨m-...⟩

563
00:28:47,269 --> 00:28:52,410
fun vaytn forn mashines mit, di, di, mit di elektrye, balaykht di veg.

